                                <emph>ysttyrajym</emph>; a scribal error.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Sam2-003-fn3" type="footnote">TKow.02: spelled <foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">כֶישְשִינְלֶיר</foreign>
                            ; a scribal error.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Sam2-003-fn4" type="footnote">TKow.02: spelled
